snippet.textDisplay:
10:04 I don't think I've ever panicked to a video before as much as I did in that moment lol. I wonder how many days are going to pass till they stop finding glitter on them.
But really, what the hell was Arin thinking! Jokes aside, how did he NOT think that was going to be a danger, little bits of glitter are like baby razors....uggh, my eyes hurt from just the though...
I'm glad they acted fast though and nothing bad happened.
But I really hope none got lost under his eyelids...so much worse then losing a contact lens.
